tps://www.arabnews.com/tags/israel"&gt;以色列&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="field-item even"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.arabnews.com/tags/chile"&gt;智利&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="field-item odd"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.arabnews.com/tags/brazil"&gt;巴西&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="field-item even"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.arabnews.com/tags/argentina"&gt;阿根廷&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Oct 2023 11:12:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.arabnews.com/node/2387961/world</guid></item></channel></rss>